Dawn Properties of Zimbabwe Profit Rises on Revaluation, Credit

-- B y   B r i a n   L a t h a m
-- 
2011-07-06T06:38:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-06/dawn-properties-of-zimbabwe-profit-rises-on-revaluation-credit.html
Dawn Properties Ltd. (DAWN) , which leases
out hotels in  Zimbabwe  to companies such as Holiday Inns UK
Inc., said profit for the year through March surged on re-
evaluation of its assets and a $6.6 million tax credit.  Net income increased to $11.7 million from $774,824 a year
earlier, the Harare-based company said in a statement published
on its  website .  Dawn will dispose of its real-estate unit, CB Richard Ellis
(Private) Ltd., and has given the realtorâ€™s management six
months to propose a buyout, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
